Section 4: Coding Tasks

Example 4.1

User

Write a Python function to group dicts by a key.
AI Response
from collections import defaultdict

def group_by(items, key):
g = defaultdict(list)
for item in items: g[item[key]].append(item)
return dict(g)

Example 4.2

User

Write a binary search function in Python.
AI Response
def binary_search(arr, target):
lo, hi = 0, len(arr) - 1
while lo <= hi:
mid = (lo + hi) // 2
if arr[mid] == target: return mid
elif arr[mid] < target: lo = mid + 1
else: hi = mid - 1
return -1

Example 4.3

User

Write a Python function to parse a URL into components.
AI Response
from urllib.parse import urlparse

def parse_url(url):
p = urlparse(url)
return {"scheme":p.scheme,"host":p.netloc,"path":p.path,"query":p.query}

print(parse_url("https://example.com/page?q=1"))

